OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny low cloud in the Lothians
OL,6,Fand Borders clearing during the
OL,7,Fmorning with bright and sunny spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping. Temperatures down a bit,
OL,9,Fbut still warm, and very warm in
OL,10,FDumfries and Galloway. Cooler breeze
OL,11,Falong east coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine warm sunny evening in
OL,14,Fall areas then a dry night with some
OL,15,Flong clear spells. Clouding over over
OL,16,Fthe Eastern Borders and East Lothians
OL,17,Fby morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
