OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA dry day. A sunny start in
OL,6,Fwest but cloud in east pushing west
OL,7,Fduring morning, then breaking up to
OL,8,Fallow some sunny intervals again.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FIt will
OL,11,Fbe a dry few days with variable cloud
OL,12,Fand some sunny spells. Mainly light
OL,13,Fwinds, and on the warm side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
